title: Selena Gomez and Justin Bieber Drop Surprise Collaboration, “Strong”
text: Justin Bieber and Selena Gomez might not be a couple anymore but that’s not to say they’ve cut all ties. The two dated on and off between 2011 and 2014, and reportedly parted ways on less than amicable terms, but they still found it in their heart to work together after all this. Over the weekend, for the briefest period of time, a Justin Bieber and Selena Gomez collaboration popped up online.
